snippet.title: FLUSTER CLUCK Gameplay Teaser Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Mines! Missiles! Turrets! Afterburners! Shields! Megafields! Decoys that go BOOM! Why does this PS4 game have cows, camels, zombies, flying saucers and poultry? Want to get the lowdown on how to earn that corporate promotion at the Chikkin Koop? Then check out this sneak peek at the FLUSTER CLUCK!  

http://www.lootentertainment.com
